; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/21386900_1558495777.jpeg" title=".jpeg" alt="WechatIMG641.jpeg" width="100%" height="auto"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">早在去年春，就有上海市的中学英语学科带头人主动同我们联系，并且有多位高中老师将我们的晨读以及外刊精读课内容放进了高中英语课堂。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">老师们反馈说，我们的课程契合了如今的英语高考需求，补充了<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">两大阅读短板：背景和思维</strong></span>。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">同诸多经验丰富的一线教师交谈后，我们了解到，<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">中学生的主要痛点是对外刊阅读有畏难情绪</strong></span>。具体讲，很多学生平时没有接触过外刊：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解外刊的叙事方法</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解英语母语人士的写作逻辑</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解这类文章的用词风格</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解了解外刊都在追什么“热点”</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">经过近一年的打磨，以及一整轮的实践运行，我们正式推出<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">中学生外刊精读</strong></span>。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/90993900_1553785974.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们的目标始终如一：我们并不做应试提分的速成，只想用很短时间，让学生知道外刊到底怎么回事：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;阅读怎么读</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;句式怎么断</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;单词怎么记</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">帮学生们找到感觉，上考场时不再发怵。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">虽是中学生版，我们依然高标准课程。<br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p styl