e="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▌<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">7天外刊精读，部分习题展示</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">根据上一期反馈，我们在这一期扩充了更多题型，涵盖各地高考要求。尤其针对写作需求做了特别设计，专治中学生写作能力薄弱。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/30044000_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">除此之外！这期开始，我们邀请老师进入我们的专属微信课程群，定期定时为同学答疑解惑。<br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">第三，200%高考词汇</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们将词汇分级归纳，分为“<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">非记不可</strong></span>”和“<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">不记也罢</strong></span>”两类。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/42099300_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“非记不可”是高考重点词汇</strong></span>，为帮助学生重点操练，我们制作了<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“派生词卡”</strong></span>， 让单词<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“开花”</strong></span>，通过词性变换、词义派生，帮助学生牢记、活记单词。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/54800400_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p st