on style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">必修</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">：</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">精读部分</strong>，</span>需要学生仔细阅读文章并听老师讲解。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">选修</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">：</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">泛读部分</strong>，</span>根据学生时间精力，推送N篇外刊相关话题文章+习题。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们希望，用逐词逐句的精读降低同学的学习门槛，听到他们需要但从传统课堂听不到的文化背景和思维方式；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们希望，从以点带面的泛读中培养同学自主阅读、广泛阅读的能力，更从中看到一个多姿多彩多面相的世界。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">在开心阅读过程中，“顺便”拿下高考。</strong></span></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section sty