<section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top: 2px solid rgb(119, 15, 15); padding-top: 3px; border-right-color: rgb(119, 15, 15); border-bottom-color: rgb(119, 15, 15); border-left-color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 2em; line-height: 2em; padding: 0px 0.5em; background-color: rgb(119, 15, 15); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">课程说明</strong></p></section><section style="width: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0.8em solid rgb(119, 15, 15); border-top: 1em solid rgb(119, 15, 15); border-right: 0.8em solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 1em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">▸&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">拉到页面最下方有免费试听课，内页更有精美讲义待你领取；</strong></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;4月-6月连续三个月，<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">4月6日开始</strong></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;">每周末更新，课程共10期</span></strong>，每课均有精美配套讲义以及高中生版特制习题（均为电子版，可供自行下载打印）；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(11, 10, 10); box-sizing: border-box;">若需转送他人（如：给自己孩子购买），<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">请在购买页面右侧点击“送好友”，下单成功后点击“赠送”，</strong><span style="color: rgb(11, 10, 10); box-sizing: border-box;">好友领取成功即可；</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">▸&nbsp;课程永久有效，可反复收听；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong>课表长这样</strong></span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/21386900_1558495777.jpeg" title=".jpeg" alt="WechatIMG641.jpeg" width="100%" height="auto"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">早在去年春，就有上海市的中学英语学科带头人主动同我们联系，并且有多位高中老师将我们的晨读以及外刊精读课内容放进了高中英语课堂。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">老师们反馈说，我们的课程契合了如今的英语高考需求，补充了<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">两大阅读短板：背景和思维</strong></span>。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">同诸多经验丰富的一线教师交谈后，我们了解到，<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">中学生的主要痛点是对外刊阅读有畏难情绪</strong></span>。具体讲，很多学生平时没有接触过外刊：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解外刊的叙事方法</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解英语母语人士的写作逻辑</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解这类文章的用词风格</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;不了解了解外刊都在追什么“热点”</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">经过近一年的打磨，以及一整轮的实践运行，我们正式推出<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">中学生外刊精读</strong></span>。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/90993900_1553785974.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们的目标始终如一：我们并不做应试提分的速成，只想用很短时间，让学生知道外刊到底怎么回事：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;阅读怎么读</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;句式怎么断</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">▸&nbsp;单词怎么记</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">帮学生们找到感觉，上考场时不再发怵。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">虽是中学生版，我们依然高标准课程。<br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">第一，&nbsp;100%高考外刊题源+100%虎课讲师亲授</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">选文均出自高考题源：《纽约时报》《经济学人》《卫报》等，话题对标高考热点：人工智能、环境污染、经济走势……</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">同寒假那期相比，这一次，我们选题更新、更广、更开放。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">所有课文均选自虎哥课堂外刊精读课，具有极强的时效性。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">除此之外，林伯虎还特别出演，倾情录制了三期特别版。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">第二，100%学科带头人出题</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">有20多年教龄的一线英语老师参与课程设计，课后习题由上海市英语学科带头人亲撰，<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">题型对标“新课标”及高考：</strong></span>&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 400px; height: 200px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; height: 200px; vertical-align: top; overflow-y: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;"><section style="overflow-x: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/34833100_1553785974.png&#39;); 