e="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▌<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">7天外刊精读，部分习题展示</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">根据上一期反馈，我们在这一期扩充了更多题型，涵盖各地高考要求。尤其针对写作需求做了特别设计，专治中学生写作能力薄弱。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/30044000_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">除此之外！这期开始，我们邀请老师进入我们的专属微信课程群，定期定时为同学答疑解惑。<br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">第三，200%高考词汇</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们将词汇分级归纳，分为“<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">非记不可</strong></span>”和“<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">不记也罢</strong></span>”两类。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/42099300_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“非记不可”是高考重点词汇</strong></span>，为帮助学生重点操练，我们制作了<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“派生词卡”</strong></span>， 让单词<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“开花”</strong></span>，通过词性变换、词义派生，帮助学生牢记、活记单词。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/54800400_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“不记也罢”</strong></span>词汇超出高考要求范围，但为了保留外刊文章的“原汁原味”，我们为学有余力的学生做了归纳总结。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">针对单词我们还有大招：<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">针对“非记不可”部分的单词，我们每月会挑选重中之重的20个单词，进行5选1，词义大测试！帮你搞懂高考重点词！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你要接受我们的挑战吗？</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/72701400_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">第四，100%精读+N00%泛读</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">重头戏要放在最后。这次，我们将课程升级为<span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">1精读+N泛读</strong></span>模式。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appNpA3AQHk1411/image/ueditor/88594000_1553785975.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">必修</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">：</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">精读部分</strong>，</span>需要学生仔细阅读文章并听老师讲解。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">选修</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">：</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">泛读部分</strong>，</span>根据学生时间精力，推送N篇外刊相关话题文章+习题。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们希望，用逐词逐句的精读降低同学的学习门槛，听到他们需要但从传统课堂听不到的文化背景和思维方式；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们希望，从以点带面的泛读中培养同学自主阅读、广泛阅读的能力，更从中看到一个多姿多彩多面相的世界。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 15, 15); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">在开心阅读过程中，“顺便”拿下高考。</strong></span></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section sty