买成功后恕不退款。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3. 本节目严禁任何形式的翻录和转载，严禁在第三方平台传播，违者将追究法律责任。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;最终解释权归虎哥课堂所有。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section>

